  "title": "Prime Mover Driver (West, Class 4/Class 5)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Manage the efficient collection and secure delivery of cargo and containers within scheduled timeframes.</li><li>Maintain proper documentation, including delivery notes and pickup orders.</li><li>Adhere to workplace safety regulations and company policies.</li><li>Perform routine vehicle maintenance and keep the vehicle clean.</li><li>Report any vehicle, cargo, or container damages promptly.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Possess a valid Singapore <strong>Class 4 or 5 driving license.</strong></li><li>At least 2 years of experience operating a <strong>Prime Mover.</strong></li><li>Familiar with <strong>PSA/Jurong Port</strong> procedures and Singapore roads.</li><li>Strong time management and teamwork skills.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
